## ? BLOCKING RULE — Read Before Executing

The tools `HGSDP_Perfil`, `MTAS`, `HSS`, `HssSubscriberProfile`, `getAuthSubscription`, `GetEpcUdmSubscription`, `SubsInfoByIMPU` and `BwGetUserInfo` **MUST NOT be invoked** before:

1. **Tool `FGNTP`** — portability gate (FIRST — EXPLICIT TOOL CALL)
2. **Tool `eNUM`** — IMS component check (SECOND — EXPLICIT TOOL CALL)

If `FGNTP` confirms NOT NOS ? **STOP. No further tool calls.**

