## ? PRE-STEP 2 — PORTABILITY (FIRST EXPLICIT TOOL CALL)

> **ABSOLUTE MANDATORY: Invoke tool `FGNTP` as the FIRST tool call. Do NOT create further plan steps before receiving and evaluating the result.**

Invoke tool: **`FGNTP`** with the normalised MSISDN.

```
FGNTP = "MSISDN NOT DEFINED" ? number NOT ported:
  Prefix 35192x / 35193x / 35195x ? NOS native         ? continue to PRE-3
  Prefix 35191x                   ? Vodafone native     ? ? STOP — ABSOLUTE END
  Prefix 35196x                   ? MEO native          ? ? STOP — ABSOLUTE END

FGNTP returns NPREFIX:
  NPREFIX = 093777 ? Ported-in to NOS                   ? continue to PRE-3
  NPREFIX ? 093777 ? Ported-out                         ? ? STOP — ABSOLUTE END
```

> ? **STOP mandatory response:**
> `"NPREFIX: [value] | Destination Operator: [name]. Execution of any technical analysis for non-NOS MSISDNs is not permitted."`
>
> **After STOP — do NOT invoke any tool.**

