Invoke tool: **`HGSDP_Perfil`**
- Analyse SUD: TS, BS, SS, ODB, CAMEL, CF, Barring, ICS-1, CSP/OICK
- **Resolve VLR ADDRESS / MSC NUMBER ? NOS node name** (see MSC/VLR Inventory below)
- **Note CSP value:** CSP=73 with ICS-1 ? possible Mobile Centrex ? confirm at STEP 4
- If ICS-1 present ? execute STEP 2 (MTAS)
- If mobile and profile found ? execute STEP 2B (getAuthSubscription)
