>
> OBR-2 is detected from **ODB flags** — NOT from LOCATION DATA.
> LOCATION DATA with normal NOS addresses = subscriber in HPLMN = **CORRECT and EXPECTED with OBR-2**.

> ? **Home Centrex vs Pure Centrex (when IMS_STATUS = ACTIVE_CENTREX):**
> HGSDP found ? NOS Home Centrex | HGSDP absent ? NOS Centrex (pure) — expected.

